{
  "stem": "7093.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "Not that we could have used the floor just the same, because the bucket at every jolt, anyway, flowed over.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "And we were sitting in everything that was in the bucket.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "On the second day in the afternoon, they were shouting that everybody picks up his luggage and get ready to get out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And we were standing there-- it was still light-- and we were standing there and waiting for the doors to open.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "And it got darker and darker.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "And when it got really dark, the train started with an extreme jolt.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "And we fell over on top of each other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "Now, it was an extremely hot summer, as I said.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "We didn't get anything to drink.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "And this went on for five days and five nights.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "People went mad.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "People were screaming.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "People collapsed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "People died.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "We had a number of death-- dead in our-- amongst us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "And we couldn't empty the buckets.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "We couldn't take out the dead.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 88,
      "text": "And that's how it-- how we arrive five days later in Auschwitz [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in Birkenau-- well, no, in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 89,
      "text": "We arrived in-- I think we arrived in Auschwitz, anyway.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 90,
      "text": "Where there was this big gate, we saw that we were arrived at the ramp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 91,
      "text": "And when we arrived, then they told us to get out very, very quickly.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 92,
      "text": "They pushed us out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 93,
      "text": "There were people in striped jackets and striped trousers who were pretty-- pushed us out pretty violently.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 94,
      "text": "And then we were separated for men and women.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 95,
      "text": "And that was the last I saw of my father.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 96,
      "text": "He said, well, maybe we can see each other another day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 97,
      "text": "But I'm afraid that was the last time I saw him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 98,
      "text": "I believe, there were rumors after the war, but I never could-- could really certify it.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
